<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-70-0949 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Geologist's Assistant combines expert system technology with numericalpattern-matching and online communication to a large database. This paperdiscusses the types of rules used for the expert system, the pattern-matchingtechnique applied, and the implementation of the system using a commercialexpert system development environment. 13 refs., 8 figs.</TEXT></DOC>